Scale the coordinate system.

### syntax

~~~ python
scale(sx, sy, sz)
scale([sx, sy, sz])
scale(size)
~~~

### parameters

sx   | amount to scale in x-direction
sy   | amount to scale in y-direction
sz   | amount to scale in z-direction
size | amount to scale in all directions

